{
  "texts": [
    "Authors' keywords network visualizationThe frequency information mentioned earlier was utilized in constructing a keyword-keyword network using the VOSviewer software.",
    "This network represents keywords as nodes and establishes edges based on the frequency of co-occurrence between pairs of keywords.",
    "By examining this network, it becomes possible to identify relationships between keywords and gain a comprehensive understanding of their connections.",
    "Moreover, the network incorporates clusters of keywords that depend on the strength of their relationship [4,171].",
    "Additionally, the frequency information aids in ranking the keywords according to their popularity, offering valuable insights into the most relevant topics within the field of social network anonymization.Following the construction of the keyword-keyword network, an analysis was conducted to unveil concealed patterns and relationships."
  ]
}